        "legal": {
          "body": "## **THE SCALES OF JUSTICE**\n\nJustice is usually about balance. \n\nOn one side of the scale, you have the **Rule of Law** (The Province's rules). \n\nOn the other side, you have the **Honour of the Crown**. This means the Government has to keep its promises to Indigenous people.\n\nIf you rule for the Crown, are you breaking a 270-year-old promise? \nIf you rule for Leo, are you ignoring the safety laws of today?\n\nThere is no easy answer.",
